These scripts and this version of PSyclone work with version 0.1 of GOcean.

In order to use PSyclone you must first add it to your PYTHONPATH:
::
    export PYTHONPATH=/path/to/PSyclone/src:${PYTHONPATH}

PSyclone can be run in the directory containing this file by 
executing, e.g.
::
    python ./runme.py

Examine the runme*.py scripts themselves for further details.

